        "body": "> what do you think about having nightly wheels\r\n\r\nSome questions around it that come to mind:\r\n\r\n- Is there a specific use case that these would be worthwhile for? First one that comes to mind is interacting with RAPIDS nightlies now that pip packaging is back, not sure if there are others I'm missing\r\n- Would these packages get published to the dask/distributed PyPI projects as pre-releases, or did you have another index in mind?\r\n\r\nHappy to take some time to look into nightly wheels if they're worth publishing, I could imagine there being some quirks around how we pin Dask/Distributed to one another (similar to the conda nightlies), but assume this wouldn't take too much effort to figure out",
